  "title": "[Immediate] - Junior Sales & Marketing Representative",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>\"Not just another event — this is where ambition meets opportunity.\"</strong></em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We’re hiring talents who are <strong>curious</strong>, <strong>driven</strong>, and <strong>excited</strong> to co-create events that connect brands with people in meaningful ways.</p>\n<p>in the field?</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>No Experience - No problem !</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>We’ll guide you, train </strong>you, and celebrate your growth every step of the way.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Your Role :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Represent the brand &amp; client</li>\n  <li>Creating revenue for the clients</li>\n  <li>Manage the team</li>\n  <li>Contributing new ideas</li>\n  <li>Involve in team meeting &amp; activities</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>The Offers :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>1-1 Mentorship Provided</li>\n  <li>Traveling Opportunities for networking</li>\n  <li>Gym membership</li>\n  <li>Workshops to groom the skillsets</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Nice To Have :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Team player with a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Customer service orientation</li>\n  <li>Ability to multitask</li>\n  <li>Creativity and initiative</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Apply now</strong> &amp; start your journey with a <strong>team that values</strong> creativity, collaboration, and career growth.</p>\n<p><em><strong>We can’t wait to see what you’ll bring to the table.</strong></em></p>",
